<div class="page_introduction">
Several Nicotiana genomes have been sequenced. <i>Nicotiana tabacum</i> is an allotetraploid that was generated by <i>Nicotiana sylvestris</i> and <i>Nicotiana tomentosiformis</i>.
The <i>Nicotiana tabacum</i> genome as well as the <i>N. sylvestris</i> and <i>N. tomentosiformis</i> genomes have been sequenced by PMI. The sequence was published in <a href="">Nature Genetics</a> in 2014.
</div>

